General.Name: Secos Group Ltd
General.Description: SECOS Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, develops, manufactures, and sells sustainable packaging materials in Oceanic, Asia, The Americas, Europe, and Africa. The company supplies biodegradable and compostable resins, packaging products, and cast films to blue-chip companies. It also develops, manufactures, and markets bioplastic resins derived from renewable resources for the packaging and plastic products industries. SECOS Group Limited is based in Mount Waverley, Australia.
